cosmetic and medical conditions including:

†    permanent hair reduction on all skin types;

†    skin rejuvenation, skin tightening and wrinkle reduction;

†    vascular lesions such as rosacea, facial spider veins, leg veins, port wine
stains, angiomas and hemangiomas;

†    all-color tattoo removal;
skin resurfacing
scars, stretch marks and warts;

